title: Trickster VR
notes: Enemies are invisible except for their armour so it's hard to tell when they are dead. A few other models are missing most notably your bow. The game works well except for the invisible stuff and the framerate is good.

title: Trickster VR
notes: Enemy and player models invisible.  Armor visible.  Playable online.  Voice chat works.

Some 3D models are not displayed such as enemy bodies and your bow. This means you can only see enemies via their armor which appears to float in the air. Despite this issue, the game does seem to run with good performance and without crashing.
